n and management</em><em> </em>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/depression-in-children/references/\">National Collaborating Centre for Mental Health, 2005</a>], which uses the World Health Organization (WHO) ICD-10 definition of depressive episodes [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/depression-in-children/references/\">WHO, 1992</a>].</p><!-- end field a7844dbf-3717-42cc-a406-d7b3b4cdbb02 --><!-- end item f1613d92-3751-4abb-86a3-5b66f2faa40d -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}